node.text: @yvon_love_cyndi 呵呵…他从小就喜欢枸杞。

“我要吃杯子里的枸杞。”
天气热，泡些菊花枸杞水，据说 “具有散风清热、平肝明目之功效”。
之后枸杞当零食，不错哦！

#Day56 #lastday #circuitbreakersg 
#AhZai #coolingdrinks #菊花枸杞茶
@sherronchua yes, 泡水就 可以了。
就单单泡而已？我也要试试，谢谢分享
@yvon_love_cyndi 呵呵…他从小就喜欢枸杞。
@alice_0787 all kids like junk food, the time will come. Hopefully he knows control and chooses well.
@leelian_chua yeah if once in a while abit junk food but daily intake healthy food I tink still ok ba.. 😛 St least got control & balance 😍
He good leh eating all e healthy food n never ask for junk food? 👍
